"672","<p style=margin:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;><font face=Times New Roman,serif lang=EN-US style=font-size:12.0pt;>Dear"
"673","Sirs:</font></p>"
"674","<p style=margin:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;text-indent:1.0in;><font face=Times New Roman,serif lang=EN-US style=font-size:12.0pt;>The above-named investment"
"675","company (the &quot;Company&quot;) herewith confirms its agreement with you as"
"676","follows:</font></p>"
"677","<p style=margin:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;text-indent:1.0in;><font face=Times New Roman,serif lang=EN-US style=font-size:12.0pt;>Dreyfus Worldwide Growth Fund"
"678","(the &quot;Fund&quot;), a series of the Company, desires to employ its capital"
"679","by investing and reinvesting the same in investments of the type and in"
"680","accordance with the limitations specified in the Fund's Prospectus and"
"681","Statement of Additional Information as from time to time in effect, copies of"
"682","which have been or will be submitted to you, and in such manner and to such"
"683","extent as from time to time may be approved by the Company's Board.&#160; The"
"684","Company desires to employ you to act as the Fund's investment adviser.</font></p>"
"685","<p style=margin:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;text-indent:1.0in;><font face=Times New Roman,serif lang=EN-US style=font-size:12.0pt;>In connection </font><font face=Times New Roman,serif lang=EN-US style=font-size:11.0pt;>with your"
"686","serving as investment adviser to the Fund</font><font face=Times New Roman,serif lang=EN-US style=font-size:12.0pt;>,"
"687","it is understood that from time to time you will employ or associate with"
"688","yourself such person or persons as you may believe to be particularly fitted to"
"689","assist you in the performance of this Agreement.&#160; Such person or persons may be"
"690","officers or employees of both you and the Company.&#160; The compensation of such"
"691","person or persons shall be paid by you and no obligation may be incurred on the"
"692","Company's behalf in any such respect.&#160; We have discussed and concur in your"
"693","employing on this basis Fayez Sarofim &amp; Co. to act as the Fund's"
"694","sub-investment adviser (the &quot;Sub-Investment Adviser&quot;) to provide"
"695","day-to-day management of the Fund's investments.</font></p>"
"696","<p style=margin:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;text-indent:1.0in;><font face=Times New Roman,serif lang=EN-US style=font-size:12.0pt;>Subject to the supervision and"
"697","approval of the Company's Board, you will provide investment management of the"
"698","Fund's portfolio in accordance with the Fund's investment objectives and"
"699","policies as stated in its Prospectus and Statement of Additional Information as"
"700","from time to time in effect.&#160; In connection therewith, you will supervise the"
"701","continuous program of investment, evaluation and, if appropriate, sale and"
"702","reinvestment of the Fund's assets conducted by the Sub-Investment Adviser.&#160; You"
"703","will furnish to the Company such statistical information, with respect to the"
"704","investments which the Fund may hold or contemplate purchasing, as the Company"
"705","may reasonably request.&#160; The Company wishes to be informed of important developments"
"706","materially affecting its portfolio and shall expect you, on your own"
"707","initiative, to furnish to the Company from time to time such information as you"
"708","may believe appropriate for this purpose.</font></p>"
"709","<a name=_bclFooter1></a><DIV>"
"710","<p style=margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;><font face=Courier New lang=EN-US style=font-size:12.0pt;>&nbsp;</font></p>"
